column2: SELECT U.up_id, S.*  FROM #upLoad U CROSS APPLY (SELECT Objid FROM   dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq( U.up_ra ,U.up_dec ,U.up_sep )) S  SELECT TOP #   p.ra,p.dec, p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj,cast(str(p.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,cast(str(p.[dec],#,#) as float) as dec,p.r,p.u,p.g,p.i,p.z,p.modelMagErr_u,p.modelMagErr_g,p.modelMagErr_r,p.modelMagErr_i,p.modelMagErr_z  FROM ..PhotoObj AS p  JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  p.u > # AND p.g > # AND p.r > # AND p.i > # AND p.z > # AND p.u < # AND p.g < # AND p.r < # AND p.i < # AND p.z < # AND (p.u - p.g) > # AND (p.g - p.r) > # AND (p.u - p.g) < # AND (p.g - p.r) < # AND ( p.type = #)   ORDER BY x.up_id
